PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of NICHOLAS OFFORD of Toronto, Ontario, to be Vice-Chairperson of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Dana W. Hanson.
